1.install the following 4 packages
libpcl1.7 : Depends: libpcl-apps1.7 but it is not going to be installed
             Depends: libpcl-io1.7 but it is not going to be installed
             Depends: libpcl-surface1.7 but it is not going to be installed
             Depends: libpcl-visualization1.7 but it is not going to be installed


2.apt-cache madison libflann-dev
3.sudo apt-get install libflann-dev=1.8.4-4.1


some childpackages conflict with others. only install the first 4

when installing pythonpcl apt will remove ros related packages which are not compatible with the 4 packages mentioned above
